sentence: died: june 09, 2015 cory allen ferguson, age 24, passed away tuesday, june 9, 2015 at riverside methodist hospital.
graduate of hilliard darby high school, class of 2010.
preceded in death by grandmother, erma mc.
survived by mother and stepfather, brenda and sidney stover; brothers, bryan (nicole) ferguson and brandon (aimee) ferguson; grandfather, joseph mc.
collister; aunts and uncles, terry, lori (jim), randy and amy; nieces and nephews, cassidy, zachary, liberty, and soon-to-be lincoln; countless friends and other family.
friends may call monday, june 15, 2015 from 11 a. m. until time of service at 1 p. m. at the tidd family funeral home, 5265 norwich st. in hilliard.
a benefit concert to assist with cory's final expenses will be friday, june 12, 2015 at ruby tuesday, 1978 summit st. in columbus.
doors open at 6 p. m. donations are also being accepted at www. gofundme.
